# Project Documentation

## Deployment Configuration

### Frontend (omniposting.com)
- Deployed on Digital Ocean droplet
- Build output: standalone Next.js application
- Nginx configuration in packages/frontend/nginx/omniposting.conf
- Deployment script in packages/frontend/scripts/deploy.sh

### Build and Deploy Process
1. Build the frontend:
   ```bash
   cd packages/frontend
   npm install
   npm run build
   ```

2. Deploy to production:
   - Build files are in .next/standalone/
   - Copy build files to /var/www/omniposting.com/
   - Configure nginx using omniposting.conf
   - Restart nginx service

### Environment Setup
- Node.js 18+
- Next.js 14
- Nginx
- PM2 for process management

### Domain Configuration
- Frontend: https://omniposting.com/
- Backend API: https://api.omniposting.com/

### Development Guidelines
- UI/UX changes must be tested locally before deployment
- Follow the dark mode theme with purple accents
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling
- Maintain component-based architecture

### Deployment Steps
1. SSH into the Digital Ocean droplet
2. Navigate to /var/www/omniposting.com
3. Pull the latest changes from the repository
4. Run the deployment script:
   ```bash
   cd packages/frontend
   ./scripts/deploy.sh
   ```

### Infrastructure
- Digital Ocean droplet hosts both frontend and backend
- Nginx serves the frontend application
- PM2 manages the Node.js processes
- SSL certificates managed through Let's Encrypt
